title: Statement by the Press Secretary on H.R. 6452 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
December 16, 2016

 



Statement by the Press Secretary on H.R. 6452





	On Friday, December 16, 2016, the President signed into law:

	H.R. 6452, the "Ensuring Access to Pacific Fisheries Act," which implements two international fisheries conventions related to the Pacific Ocean.
